criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adults diagnosed with CRPS type 1, based on Bruehl's diagnostic criteria for
             research.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Other painful conditions;

          -  Central nervous system disease;

          -  Other upper limb conditions;

          -  Diagnosis of psychiatric condition;

          -  Dyslexia and/or severe visual impairment;

          -  Presence of contraindication of tDCS (brain implant, history of severe cranial
             trauma, severe or     frequent headaches, chronic skin conditions);

          -  Sympathetic blocks for less than one month;

          -  Pregnancy.
